A Devuan Ceres base.

Building:

First:
debootstrap --keyring /root/.gnupg/pubring.gpg --arch amd64 unstable rootfs http://packages.devuan.org/merged/


Second:
chroot rootfs
gpg --keyserver pgpkeys.mit.edu --recv-key  94532124541922FB
gpg -a --export 94532124541922FB | apt-key add -
exit

And:
rm -rf rootfs/var/lib/apt/lists/* \
       rootfs/var/cache/apt/* \
       rootfs/var/cache/man/* \
       rootfs/usr/share/doc \
       rootfs/usr/share/doc-base \
       rootfs/usr/share/man \
       rootfs/usr/share/locale \ 
       rootfs/usr/share/zoneinfo

docker build -t debitux/devuan:unstable .

Running :

docker run -i -t debitux/devuan:unstable bash

